description.content:
Are you looking for a skilled developer to build, rebuild, or convert your PSD, XD, or Figma design into a fully responsive React.js or Next.js website with Tailwind CSS? You've come to the right place!


With over 5 years of experience in website development, I specialize in creating high-quality, responsive websites. I will convert your design into a fully functional React.js or Next.js site using Tailwind CSS or Bootstrap for a seamless and optimized experience.


Technologies I use include:

- HTML5, CSS3

- Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap

- JavaScript, TypeScript

- React.js, Next.js

- Material UI, Redux, Module.css

- Node.js, MongoDB

- API Integration

-WordPress


My services include:

- Building complete, functional websites from scratch

- Designing engaging and conversion-optimized landing pages

- Ensuring websites adhere to industry standards

- Improve your site's search engine ranking.

- Guarantee your site works on all major browsers.


Why choose me?

- Always here to answer your queries promptly.

- Efficient and timely project delivery

- Committed to delivering top-notch results.

- Reach out to me anytime for support.



Feel free to reach out to me via the inbox at any time.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need from me to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To begin the conversion process, I need your design files (PSD, XD, or Figma) and any specific instructions or preferences you have for the final output. Please provide all relevant assets, such as images and fonts, used in your design.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What types of design files do you accept for conversion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I accept PSD (Photoshop), XD (Adobe XD), and Figma design files for conversion to Tailwind CSS. If you have another design format, please contact me to discuss compatibility.

questionsAndAnswers.question: When you will start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will start Immediately after placing the order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide responsive design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I ensure that all conversions are fully responsive and optimized for different devices, including desktops, tablets, and mobile phones, using Tailwind CSS.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long will it take to complete the conversion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The turnaround time depends on the complexity and number of pages in your design. Typically, it takes 1-3 days for simple designs and 4-7 days for more complex projects. Please contact me for a precise estimate based on your project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer revisions if I need changes after the conversion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I offer a set number of revisions (please see the gig details for specific limits) to ensure your satisfaction with the final output. Additional revisions can be discussed if needed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I need additional pages converted after the initial order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can add extra pages at any time by purchasing a gig extra or contacting me directly to discuss your needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate the converted pages into my existing website?
